#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cindex.md:24
msgid "What is the RONL Business API?"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cindex.md:26
msgid ""
"The **RONL Business API** is a secure, multi-tenant platform that enables "
"Dutch municipalities to offer government digital services to residents. It "
"implements the **Business API Layer** pattern: a security and business-logic "
"layer that sits between a municipality's IAM system and the Operaton BPMN "
"engine."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cindex.md:35
msgid "What it does"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cindex.md:37
msgid ""
"Instead of exposing Operaton's REST API directly to municipality portals, "
"RONL Business API provides:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cindex.md:39
msgid "Secure OIDC/JWT token validation against Keycloak"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cindex.md:40
msgid ""
"Multi-tenant isolation per municipality (Utrecht, Amsterdam, Rotterdam, Den "
"Haag)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cindex.md:41
msgid "Claims mapping from JWT to BPMN process variables"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cindex.md:42
msgid "Role-based authorization (citizen, caseworker, admin)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cindex.md:43
msgid "Compliance-grade audit logging (BIO, NEN 7510, AVG/GDPR)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cindex.md:44
msgid ""
"A clean, versioned REST API (`/v1/*`) following the Dutch API Design Rules"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cindex.md:48
msgid "Architecture at a glance"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cindex.md:50
msgid ""
"Resident → Municipality Portal → Keycloak IAM → Business API → Operaton BPMN "
"Engine"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cindex.md:54
msgid ""
"The system is hosted across two platforms. Azure hosts the stateless "
"application layer (frontend, backend, PostgreSQL, Redis). A VM at `open-"
"regels.nl` hosts the services requiring deep customisation or full control "
"(Keycloak, Operaton, Caddy)."
msgstr ""

